# Keep the Docker build context tiny. Dockerfile.rendered COPYs nothing (it only installs the
# toolchain); the repo is bind-mounted at run time. Excluding these avoids sending gigabytes
# (node_modules, booted-server instances, build outputs, the artifact cache) to the daemon.
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/build
**/dist
**/target
**/.gradle
.git
.mc-test
mc-test-report
graphify-out
logs
*.log
_build.log
